NAME
  2lineart - convert image files in the current directory to 2-colour lineart
SYNOPSIS
  2lineart
DESCRIPTION
  2lineart converts every image file of a variety of formats 
  (tga, bmp, png, gif, jpeg)
  in the current working directory to a black and white (2-colour) png
  image.
  Conversion is performed using ImageMagick(1)'s convert(1) utility.
  Original files are moved to a 'backup' subfolder, which is created
  if needed.
SEE ALSO
  ImageMagick(1), convert(1)
AUTHOR
  Ryan Armstrong <software@zerker.ca>
